<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٨-<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَسَمِعْتُ أَبِي يَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَأْيَتُ النَّاسَ فِي مَسْجِدِ الْجَامِعِ كَأَنَّهُ ذَكَرَ قُلتُ الْخِضَابَ فَخَضَبَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>